Please have a look at [Distributed Executor](https://github.com/FuadEfendi/tokenizer)
- clustered, ZooKeeper-managed, it can run many tasks in parallel (Clustered Multitone)
- alternative to MapReduce (although it can generate and submit MapReduce tasks too!): 
** Web Crawl
** RSS Subscriber
** Web Ping
** Web POST
** FileServer Indexer
** Database Indexer
and many more.